NOTE: This best trades on BTC/USD on the 4H Timeframe. This is a long-only trend-following strategy that tries to enter on strong bullish moves and then stay in them until the trend meaningfully weakens. Right now, it uses 3x leverage, you can always change that input to whatever amount of leverage you like, although the max I would recommend is 5x leverage. This is also version 3.
